  <brief_title>Fenofibrate and Metformin Insulin Sensitivity in Type 2 Diabetics Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessment of Insulin Sensitivity in Type 2 Diabetics Treated With Metformin, Fenofibrate and Their Combination.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
